label("$F$",(0,0),W);
label("20'",(43,23),N);
label("62'",(49,10),E);
[/asy] The final Answer is 1208
 ### Proof
 $AB$ consists of 24 segments each of length 20 feet, and so it measures $24\cdot20=480$ feet.
